description: Tools for extracting localized content from games, and turning them into language learning content.
releaseNotes: Added support for exporting for use with [Mnemosyne](https://mnemosyne-proj.org/) and [AnyMemo](https://anymemo.org/). The text files are tab-delimited. (These exporters may get more specific support in the future, so they are not grouped together as a generic TSV export.)
